title: Any time i go to view advanced details of a match it loads a blank page.
body: the league boarder there and everything but loads a blank page

replies.body: I've seen a few reports that some players can't see their match history on the external site, and is something that's being looked into.  In the meantime, some players were able to fix this by forcing a refresh.  On the match history page try tapping Ctrl+Shift+R.  Let me know if that helps!
